<% title 'Assembly is a new way for people around the world to collectively build, launch, and grow startups.' %>
<%= track 'home.viewed' %>

<div class="masthead" style="background-image:url(<%= image_url 'pretty-people-working.jpg' %>)">
  <div class="masthead-gradient"></div>

  <div class="navbar navbar-static-top masthead-navbar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="navbar-header">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="<%= root_path %>">
          Assembly
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="navbar-right">
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
          <li>
            <a href="<%= new_user_session_path %>">
              Log in
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div><!-- .navbar -->

  <div class="container text-center">
    <h1 class="masthead-title">Build, launch, and grow a startup<br>with talented people around the world.</h1>
    <a class="play-button" href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#video-modal">
      <%= image_tag 'play.png' %>
    </a>
  </div>
</div><!-- .masthead -->

<div class="modal fade" id="video-modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
        <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/102253176?api=1" width="100%" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="https://f.vimeocdn.com/js/froogaloop2.min.js"></script>

<script>
  modal = $('#video-modal');
  player = $f(modal.find('iframe')[0]);

  modal.on('shown.bs.modal', function() {
    player.addEvent('ready', function() {
      player.api('play');
    });
  });
  modal.on('hide.bs.modal', function() {
    player.addEvent('ready', function() {
      player.api('pause');
    });
  });
</script>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-3">
      <p class="large">
        <strong>Build a product with others.</strong>
        Startups on Assembly are unlike traditional companies. They don't have investors, shareholders, or even employees. Instead, a global community creates and owns them, together.
      </p>

      <p class="large">
        <strong>Anyone can work on a product.</strong>
        The entire process is a collaborative effort, including its vision, development, design and marketing.
      </p>

      <p class="large">
        <strong>Share profit as the products you work on make money.</strong>
        Everyone shares in the success of the startups they help create. Those involved earn App Coins from others in the community for their work. At the end of each month, Assembly pays the bills and splits the proceeds among everyone with App Coins.
      </p>

      <br>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>">
          Get started
        </a>
      </div>

      <br>
      <hr>
      <br>

      <p class="text-center text-muted">
        Just have a question? <a href="mailto:assembly@helpful.io" data-helpful="assembly">Ask away!</a>
        <script src="https://assets.helpful.io/assets/widget.js"></script>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container text-center" style="margin-bottom:60px">
  <ul class="list-inline">
    <li><a href="<%= about_path %>">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="http://blog.assembly.com">Blog</a></li>
    <li><a href="<%= faq_path %>">FAQs</a></li>
    <li><a href="<%= tos_path %>">Terms</a></li>
    <li><a href="mailto:assembly@helpful.io">Contact Us</a></li>
  </ul>
</div>
